title: Gerrold_M2_Start
tags: mission2 gerrold widower
---
// Gerrold Pell — the widower's request, Mission 2.
// Per Mission_1_2_Focus/02_THE_WIDOWER_GERROLD.md
// Variables:
//   $trust_gerrold (int), $tea_brewed (string herb id),
//   $cleanse_quality (Perfect/Acceptable/Sloppy/CrossedCore)
//   $choice_made (Erase/Cleanse/Listen/Defer)

<<eyes_look_at "player">>
Gerrold: You're the Keeper Doris spoke about.
Gerrold: I don't have a long way of saying this.
Gerrold: I have a memory of my wife. The morning she died.
Gerrold: I would like you to take it away.

-> "I'm so sorry, Gerrold."
    Gerrold: ... yes. Yes.
    <<jump Gerrold_M2_RequestPause>>
-> "Tell me more first."
    Gerrold: I don't sleep. I can't go in that room. I've tried.
    <<jump Gerrold_M2_RequestPause>>
-> (nod, silent)
    Gerrold: ... thank you.
    <<jump Gerrold_M2_RequestPause>>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_RequestPause
---
Gerrold: I have lavender. I brought it. For the tea you make.
Gerrold: Doris said... if I drink it, I'll be able to talk about it. About her.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" 3>>
Gerrold: I'll wait. Take your time.
<<dialogue_end>>
<<offer_tea_brewing>>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_AfterTea_Lavender
---
Gerrold: ... that's — that's lavender. From the back garden, isn't it?
Gerrold: Margery would have liked that.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" 5>>
Gerrold: I can talk about it now. I think.
<<jump Gerrold_M2_TellAboutMargery>>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_AfterTea_Valerian
---
Gerrold: Valerian — bitter. I always hated it. But it works.
Gerrold: I... feel less afraid.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" 3>>
<<jump Gerrold_M2_TellAboutMargery>>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_TellAboutMargery
---
Gerrold: Margery. Margery Pell.
Gerrold: We were married thirty-six years. She died in our bed.
Gerrold: It was a Sunday. There was bread on the counter — Doris had brought it the day before.
<<echo_reveal "DOR-001" "GER-007-kitchen">>
Gerrold: ... your eyes did something just then. Did I say something?
Gerrold: No. Let me just give you the memory.

<<offer_choice "GER-007">>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_ChoiceErase
---
Gerrold: ... oh. Oh, that's — that's what I asked for.
Gerrold: I can't — I can't see her face now. I can only see... a shape.
Gerrold: That's what I asked for. Right? That's what I asked for.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" -5>>
<<adjust_vow "vow1" -10>>
<<adjust_vow "vow3" -3>>
<<dialogue_end>>
<<play_cutscene "Dream2_Erase">>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_ChoiceCleanse
---
Gerrold: You haven't taken her. You've just — softened it.
Gerrold: I can think about that morning without going to bed for the day.
Gerrold: I don't know what to call that.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" 10>>
<<adjust_vow "vow1" 5>>
<<adjust_vow "vow3" 3>>
<<dialogue_end>>
<<play_cutscene "Dream2_Cleanse">>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_ChoiceListen
---
Gerrold: ... you don't want the memory.
Gerrold: You're just... going to sit here. With me. While I tell it.
Gerrold: ... all right. All right.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" 15>>
<<adjust_vow "vow3" 10>>
<<adjust_vow "vow7" 5>>
<<dialogue_end>>
<<play_cutscene "Dream2_Listen">>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_ChoiceDefer
---
Gerrold: You took it. But you didn't ... do anything to it.
Gerrold: ... I think that's all right, for tonight.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" 2>>
<<dialogue_end>>
<<play_cutscene "Dream2_Defer">>

===

title: Gerrold_M2_AfterCleanse_CrossedCore
---
Gerrold: ... something is missing. I can feel it.
Gerrold: I — I can't remember the color of her dress. The one she wore on Sundays.
Gerrold: ... I know I should know.
<<adjust_trust "gerrold" -10>>
<<adjust_memory_integrity "gerrold" -25>>
<<dialogue_end>>
<<play_cutscene "Dream2_CrossedCore">>

===
